entries.s_18: You are %TU. I have been expecting you.
entries.s_22: Of course I have! Thank you for resetting that bunker for me. My colleagues will be very happy to be able to move back there. You have done us a great service. Here is your promised payment.
entries.s_28: I love Theed. I wouldn't want to live anywhere else.
entries.s_31: Sgt. Snopel told me that you are working on a job for me. I only pay for results though. Come back when you are done.
entries.s_9: Thank you. We're going to start moving back into the bunker soon.
